- HBCE Parallel Runs (Q2 & Q3) â€“ Deep Dive
  Collaborated closely with HBCE stakeholders to perform multiple rounds of parallel runs, addressing evolving user requirements and ensuring system accuracy.
  Key enhancements and solutions delivered:
  - Historical Comparison Logic: Designed an adaptive algorithm to reconcile year-on-year financial comparisons even when historical data was non-uniform or incomplete.
